CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 14th February, 1956.

The undersigned is directed to state that
Shri vengalil Krishnan Krishna Menon has assumed the office
of a Cabinet Minister without portfolio with effect from
today, the 14th February, 1956 (12 noon).
